```

- âœ… **No pip required** - Creates self-contained installation
- âœ… **Complete isolation** - Uses its own virtual environment
- âœ… **Auto-dependency handling** - Installs Python, git, curl if needed
- âœ… **Works everywhere** - Linux, macOS, Windows (WSL)

